{
  "video_id": "053JySSFyfQ",
  "title": "The Towns That Embraced Darkness to See Starlight",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 3000.0,
      "text": "This Great Big Story was made possible by Wells Fargo."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3000.0,
      "end_time": 6000.0,
      "text": "Established 1852. Re-Established 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7580.0,
      "end_time": 8389.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] There's a lot to love about living in a big, bright city."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11404.0,
      "end_time": 14154.0,
      "text": "People, culture, late-night food."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15336.0,
      "end_time": 17360.0,
      "text": "But there's something missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17360.0,
      "end_time": 20528.0,
      "text": "It's there, but you can't see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20528.0,
      "end_time": 21695.0,
      "text": "The night sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25928.0,
      "end_time": 29110.0,
      "text": "This is the story about a small town in Colorado."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29110.0,
      "end_time": 31616.0,
      "text": "- Actually, two small towns in Colorado."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31616.0,
      "end_time": 34490.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] That are devoted to space."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34490.0,
      "end_time": 37609.0,
      "text": "- [Christy] Westcliffe has a population of 564 residents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37609.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "and Silver Cliff has a population of 575."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42188.0,
      "end_time": 44439.0,
      "text": "This used to be a mining community"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44439.0,
      "end_time": 47942.0,
      "text": "and then it evolved into a railroad community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47942.0,
      "end_time": 51327.0,
      "text": "and then into a ranching community."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51327.0,
      "end_time": 53220.0,
      "text": "We're always looking to do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53220.0,
      "end_time": 55245.0,
      "text": "that will bring people into our community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55246.0,
      "end_time": 59633.0,
      "text": "and lately that seems to be we need to invest in our sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59633.0,
      "end_time": 62184.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] So they made light pollution their enemy."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62184.0,
      "end_time": 64554.0,
      "text": "They darkened their towns so that the night sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64555.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66590.00000000001,
      "text": "could become their star attraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66590.0,
      "end_time": 68431.0,
      "text": "- Have you ever seen the Milky Way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68431.0,
      "end_time": 71280.0,
      "text": "that goes from horizon to horizon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71281.0,
      "end_time": 73252.0,
      "text": "88% of the world's population"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73252.0,
      "end_time": 76354.0,
      "text": "has never seen the Milky Way."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76355.0,
      "end_time": 78980.0,
      "text": "It's the most magnificent thing in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78980.0,
      "end_time": 81890.0,
      "text": "That's what we see here."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81890.0,
      "end_time": 82898.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] But for the towns to go dark"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82898.0,
      "end_time": 85180.0,
      "text": "they needed to cover all of their lights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85180.0,
      "end_time": 86884.0,
      "text": "not just streetlamps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86884.0,
      "end_time": 89857.0,
      "text": "but the lights outside every house and ranch near town."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89857.0,
      "end_time": 91569.0,
      "text": "- That wasn't easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91569.0,
      "end_time": 94828.0,
      "text": "This is a frontier town, and I can tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94828.0,
      "end_time": 99108.0,
      "text": "frontier people don't like being told what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99108.0,
      "end_time": 102680.0,
      "text": "We had to win their hearts and minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102680.0,
      "end_time": 103798.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] It took 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103799.0,
      "end_time": 105348.0,
      "text": "They passed ordinances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105348.0,
      "end_time": 107297.0,
      "text": "raised money to cover the streetlights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107297.0,
      "end_time": 109797.0,
      "text": "and even build an observatory."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110794.0,
      "end_time": 112645.0,
      "text": "And the darker the town became,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112645.0,
      "end_time": 115503.0,
      "text": "the more people saw the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115503.0,
      "end_time": 118274.0,
      "text": "This year, the valley's dark sky was designated"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118274.0,
      "end_time": 120485.0,
      "text": "as one of the darkest in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120485.0,
      "end_time": 123394.0,
      "text": "drawing visitors from all over."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123394.0,
      "end_time": 124852.0,
      "text": "- [Man] Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124852.0,
      "end_time": 128689.0,
      "text": "- Might need a six-pack though (chuckles)."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128689.0,
      "end_time": 131668.0,
      "text": "Well I was really hopin' we'd be able to see Saturn by now."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131668.0,
      "end_time": 132918.0,
      "text": "- Yeah, me too."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133976.0,
      "end_time": 136998.0,
      "text": "- That a community would decide to dim its lights"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 136998.0,
      "end_time": 139524.0,
      "text": "and help everyone to appreciate the beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 139525.0,
      "end_time": 142480.0,
      "text": "of the night sky is an amazing thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144248.0,
      "end_time": 146557.0,
      "text": "- You come to a place like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146557.0,
      "end_time": 148724.0,
      "text": "and the stars just, burst,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 151528.0,
      "end_time": 153195.0,
      "text": "and it's remarkable."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155446.0,
      "end_time": 157700.0,
      "text": "- Not a lot of people are lucky enough to see the dark sky as our ancestors saw it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159888.0,
      "end_time": 162405.0,
      "text": "and I feel that we're a very special place"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 162405.0,
      "end_time": 164586.0,
      "text": "to be able to look at the stars"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 164586.0,
      "end_time": 167759.0,
      "text": "as people did thousands of years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 167759.0,
      "end_time": 170820.0,
      "text": "- It's a humbling thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 170820.0,
      "end_time": 173464.0,
      "text": "Suddenly you realize you can almost touch it"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 173464.0,
      "end_time": 177144.0,
      "text": "and you're now a part of the bigger universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 177144.0,
      "end_time": 179530.0,
      "text": "And so it's just a wonderful experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 179530.0,
      "end_time": 180486.0,
      "text": "to see the dark skies."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180486.0,
      "end_time": 183569.0,
      "text": "That's what we're tryin' to preserve."
    }
  ]
}